<subsection title="Deleting a project or a template" >

 <p>To delete a project or a template, navigate to the Current projects page or the Available templates page and click on the <link>'Delete this'</link> link that corresponds to project or template that you wish to delete. </p>
	<bullets>
		<item><p>Delete a project from the Current projects page.</p>
			<screenshot alttext="Deleting a project" src="resources/images/delete_a_project.png"/>
		</item>
		<item><p>Delete a template from the Available templates page. You can navigate to this page by clicking "Project templates" link on Admin menu. </p>
			<screenshot alttext="Go to available templates page" src="resources/images/installation/template_option_on_admin_menu.png"/>
